function AddHud() {
    let hudStyleElement;
    window.mazzx = window.mazzx || {};
    function formatNumberWithDots(x) {
        return x.toString().replace(/\B(?=(\d{3})+(?!\d))/g, ".");
    }
    (function () {
        const fontStyle = document.createElement('style');
        fontStyle.textContent = `
            @font-face {
                font-family: 'GothamPro Regular';
                src: url('https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fonts-Limit/Fonts/refs/heads/main/gothampro.ttf') format('truetype');
                font-weight: 400;
                font-style: normal;
                font-display: swap;
            }
        `;
        document.head.appendChild(fontStyle);

        const vignette = document.createElement('div');
        vignette.id = 'siywezz-vignette';
        vignette.style.cssText = `
            position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0;
            width: 100%; height: 100%;
            pointer-events: none;
            background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center,
                transparent 25%,
                rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 100%);
            z-index: 9997;
        `;

        const glow = document.createElement('div');
        glow.id = 'siywezz-glow';
        glow.style.cssText = `
            position: fixed;
            top: 50%; left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            width: 120vh; height: 120vh;
            background: radial-gradient(circle,
                rgba(220,220,220,0.12) 0%,
                rgba(200,200,200,0.04) 60%,
                transparent 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 9998;
        `;

        const box = document.createElement('div');
        box.id = 'siywezz-notification-full';
        box.style.cssText = `
            position: fixed;
            top: 50%; left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2.8vh;
            z-index: 9999;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
        `;

        const spinner = document.createElement('div');
        spinner.style.cssText = `
            width: 5vh;
            height: 5vh;
            border: 0.5vh solid rgba(220, 220, 220, 0.35);
            border-top: 0.5vh solid #eee;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: siywezz-rotate 1.2s linear infinite;
        `;

        const text = document.createElement('div');
        text.textContent = "che v hux";
        text.style.cssText = `
            color: #f0f0f0;
            font-family: 'GothamPro Regular', sans-serif;
            font-size: 4vh;
            text-align: center;
            text-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
            white-space: pre-line;
            line-height: 1.25;
        `;

        if (!document.getElementById('siywezz-notify-anim')) {
            const animStyle = document.createElement('style');
            animStyle.id = 'siywezz-notify-anim';
            animStyle.textContent = `@keyframes siywezz-rotate { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }`;
            document.head.appendChild(animStyle);
        }

        box.appendChild(spinner);
        box.appendChild(text);
        document.body.appendChild(vignette);
        document.body.appendChild(glow);
        document.body.appendChild(box);

        setTimeout(() => box.style.opacity = '1', 100);
        setTimeout(() => {
            box.style.opacity = '0';
            setTimeout(() => {
                [box, glow, vignette].forEach(el => {
                    if (el && el.parentNode) el.remove();
                });
            }, 400);
        }, 5000);
    })();

    function createHud() {

#app .capture-table__col-kills,

        document.head.appendChild(hudStyleElement);
        const hudElement = document.createElement("div");
        hudElement.id = 'SiywezzHudContainer';
        hudElement.innerHTML = `
      <div class="Siywezz-Hud">
        <div class="Siywezz-HudTop">
          <div class="Siywezz-Logo">
            <img src="${SiywezzConfig.logo[1]}">
            <div class="Siywezz-Bonus">x3</div>
          </div>
          <div class="Siywezz-Main">
            <div class="Siywezz-Params">
              <div class="Siywezz-Cash"><img src="${SiywezzConfig.icons.cash}"><span>0</span></div>
              <div class="Siywezz-Params__all">
                <div class="Siywezz-Param health">
                  <img src="${SiywezzConfig.icons.health}" class="siywezz-param__icon">
                  <div class="Siywezz-Param-Progress">
                    <div class="Siywezz-Progress__Values" style="width:100%"><img src="${SiywezzConfig.icons.circle}" class="circle"></div>
                  </div>
                  <span class="Siywezz-Param-Values">100</span>
                </div>
                <div class="Siywezz-Param armour">
                  <img src="${SiywezzConfig.icons.armour}" class="siywezz-param__icon">
                  <div class="Siywezz-Param-Progress">
                    <div class="Siywezz-Progress__Values" style="width:0%"><img src="${SiywezzConfig.icons.circle}" class="circle"></div>
                  </div>
                  <span class="Siywezz-Param-Values">0</span>

                <div class="Siywezz-Param hunger">
                  <img src="${SiywezzConfig.icons.hunger}" class="siywezz-param__icon">

                    <div class="Siywezz-Progress__Values" style="width:100%"><img src="${SiywezzConfig.icons.circle}" class="circle"></div>
                  </div>

                  <img src="${SiywezzConfig.icons.breath}" class="siywezz-param__icon">

                    <div class="Siywezz-Progress__Values" style="width:100%"><img src="${SiywezzConfig.icons.circle}" class="circle"></div>
                  </div>
                  <span class="Siywezz-Param-Values">100</span>

              <img src="${SiywezzConfig.weapon[0]}" class="Siywezz-Weapon_icon">
              <div class="Siywezz-Weapon_ammo"><span class="Ammo-in-clip">0</span><span class="Ammo-full">/0</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="Siywezz-Wanted">
            <img src="${SiywezzConfig.icons.weapon_back}" class="Siywezz-Wanted_back">
            <div class="Wanted_row">
              <img src="${SiywezzConfig.icons.inactive_wanted}">
              <img src="${SiywezzConfig.icons.inactive_wanted}">
              <img src="${SiywezzConfig.icons.inactive_wanted}">
              <img src="${SiywezzConfig.icons.inactive_wanted}">
              <img src="${SiywezzConfig.icons.inactive_wanted}">
              <img src="${SiywezzConfig.icons.inactive_wanted}">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="Siywezz-HudBottom">
          <div class="Siywezz-Freeze">
            <span class="Siywezz-Freeze_text">Freeze:</span>
            <span class="Siywezz-Freeze_value">100</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    `;
        document.body.appendChild(hudElement);
    }

    const updateFunctions = {
        show: (value) => {
            const hudEl = document.querySelector(".Siywezz-Hud");
            if (hudEl) hudEl.style.display = +value >= 1 ? "" : "none";
        },
        showBars: (value) => {
            updateFunctions.show(value);
        },
        weapon: (value) => {
            const weaponIcon = document.querySelector(".Siywezz-Weapon_icon");
            if (weaponIcon) {
                const weaponSrc = SiywezzConfig.weapon[value];
                if (weaponSrc) {
                    weaponIcon.src = weaponSrc;
                }
            }
            const ammoEls = document.querySelectorAll(".Siywezz-Weapon_ammo span");
            ammoEls.forEach(el => {
                if (el) el.style.display = value >= 16 ? "" : "none";
            });
        },
        health: (value) => {
            updateParam("health", value);
        },
        armour: (value) => {
            updateParam("armour", value);
        },
        hunger: (value) => {
            updateParam("hunger", value);
        },
        breath: (value) => {
            const breathWrapper = document.querySelector(".Siywezz-Param.breath .Siywezz-Param-Progress")?.parentElement;
            if (breathWrapper) breathWrapper.style.display = value < 99 ? "" : "none";
            updateParam("breath", value);
        },
        bonus: (bonusValue) => {
            const bonusEl = document.querySelector(".Siywezz-Bonus");
            if (bonusEl) {
                if (bonusValue <= 1) {
                    bonusEl.style.display = "none";
                } else {
                    bonusEl.style.display = "";
                    bonusEl.textContent = `x${bonusValue}`;
                }
            }
        },
        server: (serverId) => {
            const serverWrapper = document.querySelector(".Siywezz-Logo img");
            if (serverWrapper) {
                if (serverId <= 0) {
                    serverWrapper.style.display = "none";
                } else {
                    serverWrapper.style.display = "";
                    const serverLogo = SiywezzConfig.logo[serverId];
                    if (serverLogo) {
                        serverWrapper.src = serverLogo;
                    }
                }
            }
        },
        money: (value) => {
            const moneyEl = document.querySelector(".Siywezz-Cash span");
            if (moneyEl) moneyEl.textContent = formatNumberWithDots(value);
        },
        wanted: (value) => {
            const wantedIcons = document.querySelectorAll(".Wanted_row img");
            for (let i = 0; i < wantedIcons.length; i++) {
                wantedIcons[i].src = (i < value)
                    ? SiywezzConfig.icons.active_wanted
                    : SiywezzConfig.icons.inactive_wanted;
            }
            const wantedWrapper = document.querySelector(".Siywezz-Wanted");
            if (wantedWrapper) {
                wantedWrapper.style.display = (value > 0) ? "" : "none";
            }
        },
        ammoInClip: (value) => {
            const inClipEl = document.querySelector(".Ammo-in-clip");
            if (inClipEl) inClipEl.textContent = value;
        },
        totalAmmo: (value) => {
            const totalAmmoEl = document.querySelector(".Ammo-full");
            if (totalAmmoEl) totalAmmoEl.textContent = "/" + value;
        },
        freeze: (value) => {
            const freezeValueEl = document.querySelector(".Siywezz-Freeze_value");
            if (freezeValueEl) {
                const formattedValue = String(value).padStart(3, '0');
                freezeValueEl.textContent = formattedValue;
            }
        },
    };

    function onInfoChange(type, value) {
        if (updateFunctions[type]) {
            updateFunctions[type](value);
        }
    }

    function updateParam(paramClass, value) {
        const paramElement = document.querySelector(`.Siywezz-Param.${paramClass}`);
        if (paramElement) {
            const progressBar = paramElement.querySelector(".Siywezz-Progress__Values");
            const valueText = paramElement.querySelector(".Siywezz-Param-Values");
            progressBar.style.width = `${value}%`;
            valueText.textContent = value;
        }
    }

    function initializeHudProxy() {
        const checkInterval = setInterval(() => {
            if (typeof window.interface === "function" && window.interface("Hud").info) {
                clearInterval(checkInterval);
                const hudInfo = window.interface("Hud").info;
                const clonedHudInfo = JSON.parse(JSON.stringify(hudInfo));
                window.interface("Hud").info = new Proxy(clonedHudInfo, {
                    set(target, prop, value) {
                        if (target[prop] !== value) {
                            target[prop] = value;
                            onInfoChange(prop, value);
                        }
                        return Reflect.set(target, prop, value);
                    }
                });
                window.interface("Hud").setServer = (serverId) => {
                    onInfoChange("server", serverId);
                    window.interface("Hud").server = serverId;
                };
                window.interface("Hud").setBonus = (bonusValue) => {
                    onInfoChange("bonus", bonusValue);
                    window.interface("Hud").bonus = bonusValue;
                };
                createHud();
                const props = ['health', 'armour', 'hunger', 'breath', 'money', 'wanted', 'ammoInClip', 'totalAmmo', 'freeze', 'weapon', 'show'];
                props.forEach(prop => {
                    if (prop in hudInfo && updateFunctions[prop]) {
                        updateFunctions[prop](hudInfo[prop]);
                    }
                });
                if ('server' in window.interface("Hud")) updateFunctions.server(window.interface("Hud").server);
                if ('bonus' in window.interface("Hud")) updateFunctions.bonus(window.interface("Hud").bonus);
            }
        }, 100);
    }

    initializeHudProxy();
    window.onInfoChange = onInfoChange;
}

AddHud();


(function () {
    if (window.__greenZoneFixed) return;
    window.__greenZoneFixed = true;
    const style = document.createElement('style');
    style.textContent = `
        [class*="green"], [class*="zone"], .hud-radmir-greenzone,
        .green-zone, .gzone, .map__greenzone, .map-greenzone,
        svg[class*="zone"], svg[class*="green"],
        #app .hud-circle-green, #app .hud-round-green {
            display: none !important;
            opacity: 0 !important;
            visibility: hidden !important;
        }
    `;
    document.head.appendChild(style);
    const customZone = document.createElement('div');
    customZone.className = 'Siywezz-Zone';
    customZone.innerHTML = `
        <img src="data:image/png;base64," 
         style="width: 3.5vh; height: 4.5vh;">
    `;
    customZone.style.cssText = `
        position: absolute;
        left: 3%;
        bottom: 5vh;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        display: none;
        z-index: 999999;
    `;
    document.body.appendChild(customZone);
    const initInterval = setInterval(() => {
        if (typeof window.interface !== 'function') return;
        const hud = window.interface('Hud');
        if (!hud || !hud.showGreenZoneTab || !hud.hideGreenZoneTab) return;
        clearInterval(initInterval);
        const origShow = hud.showGreenZoneTab;
        const origHide = hud.hideGreenZoneTab;
        hud.showGreenZoneTab = function () {
            customZone.style.display = '';
            return origShow.apply(this, arguments);
        };
        hud.hideGreenZoneTab = function () {
            customZone.style.display = 'none';
            return origHide.apply(this, arguments);
        };
    }, 100);
})();
